<p class="center taxobox_classification"><b><span style="font-style: normal"><span lang="la" xml:lang="la"><i>Clangula</i></span></span></b><br />
<span class="rnormal"><small><b><a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Elford_Leach" title="William Elford Leach">Leach</a>, <a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/1819" title="1819">1819</a></b></small></span></p>
